# Note: package-lock.json is debated, but often kept. 
# However, if you want to ensure exact versions, keep it. 
# If you want to rely on package.json, ignore it. 
# I will NOT ignore package-lock.json by default as it is best practice to keep it, 
# but removing it from ignore list here.

